      {
        "paragraphContent": "ἀποστέλλω",
        "level": 0,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "“to send forth to service in the kingdom of God with full authority (grounded in God).”",
        "level": 1,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "ἀποστέλλειν希腊语的基本含义是 “送出”, 在新约中指“以完全的权柄（以神为根基）派遣到神的国度中服务”。",
        "level": 1,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "——K.H. Rengstorf, 新约神学词典（TDNT）, 1964",
        "level": 1,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "Even more significant is its meaning, for the NT uses this noun only in the sense of “messenger,” and partic. as the fixed designation of a definite Christian office新约只在 \"信使 \"的意义上使用这个名词，尤其是作为一个确定的基督徒职位的固定名称。",
        "level": 1,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "——M. Silva, Ed., 新约神学与注释新国际词典(NIDNTTE), 2014",
        "level": 1,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "Paul, an apostle of Christ Jesus by the will of God,",
        "level": 0,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "To the saints who are at Ephesus and who are faithful in Christ Jesus: Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.",
        "level": 0,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "奉神旨意做基督耶稣使徒的保罗，",
        "level": 0,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "写信给在以弗所的圣徒，就是在基督耶稣里有忠心的人。 愿恩惠、平安从神我们的父和主耶稣基督归于你们！",
        "level": 0,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "Παῦλος ἀπόστολος Χριστοῦ Ἰησοῦ διὰ θελήματος θεοῦ τοῖς ἁγίοις τοῖς οὖσιν [ἐν Ἐφέσῳ] καὶ πιστοῖς ἐν Χριστῷ Ἰησοῦ·",
        "level": 0,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "χάρις ὑμῖν καὶ εἰρήνη ἀπὸ θεοῦ πατρὸς ἡμῶν καὶ κυρίου Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ.",
        "level": 0,
        "content_type": ""
      },
      {
        "paragraphContent": "——以弗所书1:1-2",
        "level": 0,
        "content_type": ""
      }
    ]
  },
